/* LottoSphere — client-side JS generator
   - Loads CSV or sample
   - Computes freq and lastSeen
   - Generates sets by method
*/

const sampleCSV = `date,w1,w2,w3,w4,w5,red
2025-09-20,3,14,27,44,63,9
2025-09-17,7,12,23,34,58,10
2025-09-13,1,9,16,26,46,5
2025-09-10,10,22,28,47,60,14
2025-09-06,4,18,29,30,66,2
2025-09-03,5,11,20,35,61,22
2025-08-30,2,13,24,37,67,11
2025-08-27,6,19,21,41,59,3
2025-08-23,8,15,25,36,64,7
2025-08-20,17,32,38,45,68,12
`; // NOTE: only a few rows to let UI run

const lotteryPresets = {
  powerball: {whiteCount:5, whiteMax:69, redMax:26},
  megamillions: {whiteCount:5, whiteMax:70, redMax:25}
};

let dataset = []; // array of draws {date, whites:[], red}
let stats = null;

function parseCSV(text){
  const lines = text.trim().split(/\r?\n/).map(l => l.trim()).filter(Boolean);
  let rows = [];
  for(let i=0;i<lines.length;i++){
    const parts = lines[i].split(',').map(p=>p.trim());
    // try to find where numbers start (skip header)
    if(i===0 && parts.some(p=>/w\d|white|red|date/i.test(p))) continue;
    // assume last column is red, previous N columns are whites
    if(parts.length < 6) continue;
    const date = parts[0];
    const nums = parts.slice(1).map(x=>parseInt(x,10)).filter(n=>!isNaN(n));
    if(nums.length < 6) continue;
    rows.push({date, whites: nums.slice(0,5).sort((a,b)=>a-b), red: nums[5]});
  }
  return rows;
}

function computeStats(draws, whiteMax, redMax, whiteCount){
  // frequency for whites and red, and lastSeen index
  const freqW = Array(whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  const freqR = Array(redMax+1).fill(0);
  const lastSeenW = Array(whiteMax+1).fill(-1);
  const lastSeenR = Array(redMax+1).fill(-1);

  for(let i=0;i<draws.length;i++){
    const d = draws[i];
    d.whites.forEach(w => { if(w>=1 && w<=whiteMax){ freqW[w]++; lastSeenW[w]=i; }});
    const r = d.red;
    if(r>=1 && r<=redMax){ freqR[r]++; lastSeenR[r]=i; }
  }
  // compute "gap" (how many draws since last seen). lastSeen -1 -> very overdue
  const total = draws.length;
  const gapW = lastSeenW.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx));
  const gapR = lastSeenR.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx));
  return {freqW,freqR,gapW,gapR,total};
}

function normalize(arr){
  const max = Math.max(...arr.slice(1));
  if(max<=0) return arr.map(_=>1);
  return arr.map(v=> (v / max) + 0.001 );
}

function pickNumbers(method, statsObj, whiteCount, whiteMax, redMax, includeRed){
  const {freqW,freqR,gapW,gapR,total} = statsObj;
  const normFreqW = normalize(freqW);
  const normGapW = normalize(gapW);
  const weightW = [];

  for(let n=0;n<=whiteMax;n++){
    // strategy weighting
    let w = 1;
    if(method === 'hot') w = normFreqW[n];
    else if(method === 'cold') w = 1/(normFreqW[n] || 0.0001);
    else if(method === 'overdue') w = normGapW[n];
    else if(method === 'random') w = 1;
    else if(method === 'weighted') w = (normFreqW[n]*0.6) + (normGapW[n]*0.8);
    else if(method === 'mixed') w = (normFreqW[n]*0.6) + (1/(normFreqW[n]||0.0001)*0.3) + (normGapW[n]*0.5);
    weightW.push(Math.max(0.001,w));
  }

  function sampleUnique(weights, k, maxN){
    const chosen = new Set();
    // cumulative sampler
    const candidates = [];
    for(let i=1;i<=maxN;i++) candidates.push({n:i,w:weights[i] || 0.001});
    while(chosen.size < k){
      const totalW = candidates.reduce((s,c)=> s + (chosen.has(c.n)?0:c.w),0);
      if(totalW <= 0.0001){
        // fallback: random remaining
        for(let i=1;i<=maxN && chosen.size<k;i++) if(!chosen.has(i)) chosen.add(i);
        break;
      }
      let r = Math.random()*totalW;
      let acc=0;
      for(const c of candidates){
        if(chosen.has(c.n)) continue;
        acc += c.w;
        if(r <= acc){ chosen.add(c.n); break; }
      }
    }
    return Array.from(chosen).sort((a,b)=>a-b);
  }

  const whites = sampleUnique(weightW, whiteCount, whiteMax);

  let red = null;
  if(includeRed){
    const weightR = [];
    for(let n=0;n<=redMax;n++){
      let w = 1;
      if(method === 'hot') w = (freqR[n] || 0.001);
      else if(method === 'cold') w = 1/((freqR[n]||0.001));
      else if(method === 'overdue') w = (gapR[n] || 0.001);
      else if(method === 'random') w = 1;
      else if(method === 'weighted') w = ((freqR[n]||0.001)*0.6) + ((gapR[n]||0.001)*0.8);
      else if(method === 'mixed') w = ((freqR[n]||0.001)*0.6) + (1/((freqR[n]||0.001))*0.3) + ((gapR[n]||0.001)*0.5);
      weightR.push(Math.max(0.001,w));
    }
    const pickR = sampleUnique(weightR, 1, redMax)[0];
    red = pickR;
  }

  return {whites, red};
}

function prettySet(s){
  return s.whites.map(n=>String(n).padStart(2,' ')).join(' ') + (s.red ? `  | ${String(s.red).padStart(2,' ')}` : '');
}

document.getElementById('loadSample').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
  dataset = parseCSV(sampleCSV);
  applyPreset('powerball');
  updateSummary();
  alert('Loaded sample dataset (demo only). For accurate suggestions, upload official past draws CSV.');
});

document.getElementById('csvfile').addEventListener('change', (ev)=>{
  const f = ev.target.files[0];
  if(!f) return;
  const reader = new FileReader();
  reader.onload = e => {
    try{
      dataset = parseCSV(e.target.result);
      applyPreset(document.getElementById('lotteryType').value);
      updateSummary();
      alert('CSV loaded: ' + dataset.length + ' draws.');
    }catch(err){ alert('Error parsing CSV: ' + err.message); }
  };
  reader.readAsText(f);
});

document.getElementById('lotteryType').addEventListener('change', (e)=>{
  const v = e.target.value;
  document.getElementById('customBox').style.display = v==='custom' ? 'block' : 'none';
  applyPreset(v);
});

function applyPreset(key){
  if(key === 'custom'){
    // wait for user input
    return;
  }
  const p = lotteryPresets[key];
  document.getElementById('customParams').value = `${p.whiteCount},${p.whiteMax},${p.redMax}`;
}

document.getElementById('analyze').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
  const method = document.getElementById('method').value;
  const count = Math.max(1, Math.min(200, parseInt(document.getElementById('count').value) || 10));
  const includeRed = document.getElementById('includeRed').value === 'true';

  // resolve lottery params
  let whiteCount = 5, whiteMax = 69, redMax = 26;
  const lt = document.getElementById('lotteryType').value;
  if(lt === 'custom'){
    const parts = (document.getElementById('customParams').value || '').split(',').map(s=>parseInt(s.trim(),10));
    if(parts.length >= 3 && parts.every(n=>!isNaN(n))){
      whiteCount = parts[0]; whiteMax = parts[1]; redMax = parts[2];
    } else { alert('Custom params invalid. Use format: whites,whiteMax,redMax'); return; }
  } else {
    const p = lotteryPresets[lt];
    whiteCount = p.whiteCount; whiteMax = p.whiteMax; redMax = p.redMax;
  }

  if(dataset.length < 1){
    if(!confirm('No dataset loaded. Generator will use empty/default stats (pure random). Continue?')) return;
  }

  stats = computeStats(dataset, whiteMax, redMax, whiteCount);
  const resultsArea = document.getElementById('resultsArea');
  resultsArea.innerHTML = '';

  // show quick stats
  updateSummary();

  const generated = [];
  for(let i=0;i<count;i++){
    const s = pickNumbers(method, stats, whiteCount, whiteMax, redMax, includeRed);
    generated.push(s);
    const div = document.createElement('div');
    div.className = 'set card';
    div.style.padding = '10px';
    div.style.display = 'flex';
    div.style.alignItems = 'center';
    const balls = document.createElement('div');
    balls.style.display='flex'; balls.style.gap='8px';
    s.whites.forEach(w=>{
      const b = document.createElement('div');
      b.className='ball'; b.textContent = w;
      balls.appendChild(b);
    });
    if(s.red){
      const br = document.createElement('div');
      br.className='ball'; br.style.background='linear-gradient(180deg,#fca5a5,#f87171)'; br.textContent = s.red;
      balls.appendChild(br);
    }
    const meta = document.createElement('div');
    meta.style.marginLeft='10px';
    meta.innerHTML = `<div style="font-weight:700">${prettySet(s)}</div><div class="meta">Method: ${method} • Set #${i+1}</div>`;
    div.appendChild(balls);
    div.appendChild(meta);
    resultsArea.appendChild(div);
  }

  // save for download
  resultsArea.dataset.generated = JSON.stringify(generated);
});

document.getElementById('downloadCSV').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
  const data = document.getElementById('resultsArea').dataset.generated;
  if(!data){ alert('No results to download. Generate sets first.'); return; }
  const arr = JSON.parse(data);
  let csv = 'w1,w2,w3,w4,w5,red\n';
  arr.forEach(s=>{
    csv += s.whites.join(',') + ',' + (s.red || '') + '\n';
  });
  const blob = new Blob([csv], {type:'text/csv'});
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  const a = document.createElement('a');
  a.href = url; a.download = 'lottosphere_sets.csv';
  document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); a.remove(); URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
});

function updateSummary(){
  const s = document.getElementById('summary');
  if(!dataset || dataset.length===0){
    s.textContent = 'No data loaded.';
    document.getElementById('quickStats').innerHTML = '';
    return;
  }
  // default use powerball params for summary if unknown
  const lt = document.getElementById('lotteryType').value;
  let whiteCount=5, whiteMax=69, redMax=26;
  if(lt==='custom'){
    const parts = (document.getElementById('customParams').value || '').split(',').map(p=>parseInt(p,10));
    if(parts.length>=3){ whiteCount=parts[0]; whiteMax=parts[1]; redMax=parts[2]; }
  } else { const p=lotteryPresets[lt]; whiteCount=p.whiteCount; whiteMax=p.whiteMax; redMax=p.redMax; }

  const computed = computeStats(dataset, whiteMax, redMax, whiteCount);
  const freqW = computed.freqW.slice(1); // ignore zero index
  // find top 5 hot and top 5 overdue
  const idxs = freqW.map((f,i)=>({n:i+1,f})).sort((a,b)=>b.f-a.f);
  const hot = idxs.slice(0,5).map(x=>x.n);
  const gaps = computed.gapW.slice(1).map((g,i)=>({n:i+1,g})).sort((a,b)=>b.g-a.g);
  const overdue = gaps.slice(0,5).map(x=>x.n);

  s.textContent = `${dataset.length} draws loaded • Whites 1–${whiteMax} • Red 1–${redMax}`;
  const qs = document.getElementById('quickStats');
  qs.innerHTML = '';
  const p1 = document.createElement('div'); p1.className='pill'; p1.textContent = 'Hot: ' + hot.join(', ');
  const p2 = document.createElement('div'); p2.className='pill'; p2.textContent = 'Overdue: ' + overdue.join(', ');
  qs.appendChild(p1); qs.appendChild(p2);
}

</script>
</body>
</html>

const sampleDraws = {
  powerball:[
    [3,14,27,44,63,9],
    [7,12,23,34,58,10],
    [1,9,16,26,46,5],
    [10,22,28,47,60,14],
    [4,18,29,30,66,2]
  ],

    [5,11,20,36,61,15],
    [2,13,24,37,67,22],
    [8,15,25,36,64,7]
  ]
};

// Generate numbers function
function generateNumbers(lottery, method, count, includeSpecial){
  let whiteCount=5, whiteMax=69, specialMax=26;
  if(lottery==='mega'){whiteMax=70; specialMax=25;}
  if(lottery==='custom'){
    const parts=document.getElementById('customParams').value.split(',').map(Number);
    if(parts.length>=3){whiteCount=parts[0];whiteMax=parts[1];specialMax=parts[2];}
  }
  const draws = sampleDraws[lottery] || [];
  // Compute frequency
  const freq = Array(whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  draws.forEach(d=>d.slice(0,whiteCount).forEach(n=>freq[n]++));
  const results=[];
  for(let i=0;i<count;i++){
    let set=[];
    while(set.length<whiteCount){
      let n=Math.floor(Math.random()*whiteMax)+1;
      if(!set.includes(n)) set.push(n);
    }
    set.sort((a,b)=>a-b);
    let special=null;
    if(includeSpecial==='true') special=Math.floor(Math.random()*specialMax)+1;
    results.push({whites:set,special});
  }
  return results;
}

// Render numbers
function renderNumbers(results, containerId){
  const container=document.getElementById(containerId);
  container.innerHTML='';
  results.forEach((s,i)=>{
    const div=document.createElement('div'); div.className='set';
    s.whites.forEach(n=>{
      const b=document.createElement('div'); b.className='ball'; b.textContent=n; div.appendChild(b);
    });
    if(s.special){
      const b=document.createElement('div'); b.className='ball red'; b.textContent=s.special; div.appendChild(b);
    }
    container.appendChild(div);
  });
}

// Frequency chart
function renderFreqChart(results, canvasId){
  const freq = {};
  results.forEach(s=>s.whites.forEach(n=>freq[n]= (freq[n]||0)+1 ));
  const ctx=document.getElementById(canvasId).getContext('2d');
  new Chart(ctx,{
    type:'bar',
    data:{
      labels:Object.keys(freq),
      datasets:[{label:'Frequency',data:Object.values(freq),backgroundColor:'#66fcf1'}]
    },
    options:{plugins:{legend:{display:false}},scales:{y:{beginAtZero:true}}}
  });
}

// Generate button
document.getElementById('generateBtn').addEventListener('click',()=>{

  const method=document.getElementById('method').value;
  const count=parseInt(document.getElementById('setCount').value)||10;
  const includeSpecial=document.getElementById('includeSpecial').value;
  const results=generateNumbers(lottery,method,count,includeSpecial);
  renderNumbers(results,'lotteryResults');
  renderFreqChart(results,'freqChart');
});

const sampleDraws = {
  powerball:[
    [3,14,27,44,63,9],
    [7,12,23,34,58,10],
    [1,9,16,26,46,5],
    [10,22,28,47,60,14],

// Generate numbers
function generateNumbers(lottery, method, count, includeSpecial){
  let whiteCount=5, whiteMax=69, specialMax=26;
  if(lottery==='mega'){whiteMax=70; specialMax=25;}
  if(lottery==='custom'){
    const parts=document.getElementById('customParams').value.split(',').map(Number);
    if(parts.length>=3){whiteCount=parts[0];whiteMax=parts[1];specialMax=parts[2];}
  }
  const draws = sampleDraws[lottery] || [];
  const freq = Array(whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  draws.forEach(d=>d.slice(0,whiteCount).forEach(n=>freq[n]++));
  const results=[];
  for(let i=0;i<count;i++){
    let set=[];
    while(set.length<whiteCount){
      let n=Math.floor(Math.random()*whiteMax)+1;
      if(!set.includes(n)) set.push(n);
    }
    set.sort((a,b)=>a-b);
    let special=null;
    if(includeSpecial==='true') special=Math.floor(Math.random()*specialMax)+1;
    results.push({whites:set,special});
  }
  return results;
}

// Render numbers
function renderNumbers(results, containerId){
  const container=document.getElementById(containerId);
  container.innerHTML='';
  results.forEach((s,i)=>{
    const div=document.createElement('div'); div.className='set';
    s.whites.forEach(n=>{
      const b=document.createElement('div'); b.className='ball'; b.textContent=n; div.appendChild(b);
    });
    if(s.special){
      const b=document.createElement('div'); b.className='ball red'; b.textContent=s.special; div.appendChild(b);
    }
    container.appendChild(div);
  });
}

// Frequency chart
function renderFreqChart(results, canvasId){
  const freq = {};
  results.forEach(s=>s.whites.forEach(n=>freq[n]= (freq[n]||0)+1 ));
  const ctx=document.getElementById(canvasId).getContext('2d');
  new Chart(ctx,{
    type:'bar',
    data:{
      labels:Object.keys(freq),
      datasets:[{label:'Frequency',data:Object.values(freq),backgroundColor:'#66fcf1'}]
    },
    options:{plugins:{legend:{display:false}},scales:{y:{beginAtZero:true}}}
  });
}

// Generate button
document.getElementById('generateBtn').addEventListener('click',()=>{

  const method=document.getElementById('method').value;
  const count=parseInt(document.getElementById('setCount').value)||10;
  const includeSpecial=document.getElementById('includeSpecial').value;
  const results=generateNumbers(lottery,method,count,includeSpecial);
  renderNumbers(results,'lotteryResults');

});

// parse CSV text into draws array
function parseCSVText(text, preset){
  const lines = text.split(/\r?\n/).map(l=>l.trim()).filter(Boolean);
  const rows = [];
  for (let i=0;i<lines.length;i++){
    const parts = lines[i].split(',').map(p=>p.trim()).filter(p=>p!=='');
    if (parts.length < preset.whiteCount) continue;
    // if first cell is non-date header, try to skip
    if (i===0 && parts.some(p=>/date|w1|white/i.test(p))) continue;
    // if first token looks like a date, remove or keep
    let nums = parts.slice( (isNaN(Number(parts[0])) ? 1 : 0) ).map(n=>Number(n)).filter(n=>!isNaN(n));
    if (nums.length < preset.whiteCount) continue;
    rows.push(nums);
  }
  return rows;
}

// compute frequency and gap (overdue)
function computeStats(draws, whiteMax, specialMax, whiteCount){
  const freqW = new Array(whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  const freqS = specialMax>0? new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0) : null;
  const lastSeenW = new Array(whiteMax+1).fill(-1);
  const lastSeenS = specialMax>0? new Array(specialMax+1).fill(-1) : null;
  for (let i=0;i<draws.length;i++){
    const row = draws[i];
    for (let j=0;j<whiteCount && j<row.length;j++){
      const n = row[j];
      if (n>=1 && n<=whiteMax){ freqW[n]++; lastSeenW[n]=i; }
    }
    if (specialMax>0 && row.length>whiteCount){
      const s = row[whiteCount];
      if(s>=1 && s<=specialMax){ freqS[s]++; lastSeenS[s]=i; }
    }
  }
  const total = draws.length;
  const gapW = lastSeenW.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx));
  const gapS = lastSeenS? lastSeenS.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx)) : null;
  return {freqW, freqS, gapW, gapS, total};
}

// normalize array (index 1..N)
function normalize(arr){
  const a = arr.slice();
  const max = Math.max(...a.slice(1));
  if (max <= 0) return a.map(_=>1);
  return a.map(v => (v / max) + 0.001);
}

// sampling unique numbers weighted
function sampleUnique(weights, k, maxN){
  const chosen = new Set();
  const candidates = [];
  for (let i=1;i<=maxN;i++) candidates.push({n:i,w:Math.max(0.0001, weights[i]||0.0001)});
  while (chosen.size < k){
    const totalW = candidates.reduce((s,c)=> s + (chosen.has(c.n)?0:c.w), 0);
    if (totalW <= 0.0001){
      for (let i=1;i<=maxN && chosen.size<k;i++) if (!chosen.has(i)) chosen.add(i);
      break;
    }
    let r = Math.random()*totalW, acc=0;
    for (const c of candidates){
      if (chosen.has(c.n)) continue;
      acc += c.w;
      if (r <= acc){ chosen.add(c.n); break; }
    }
  }
  return Array.from(chosen).sort((a,b)=>a-b);
}

// generate one set based on method
function generateSet(method, stats, whiteCount, whiteMax, specialMax, includeSpecial){
  const {freqW, freqS, gapW, gapS} = stats;
  const normFreq = normalize(freqW);
  const normGap = normalize(gapW);
  const weightW = [];
  for (let n=0;n<=whiteMax;n++){
    let w = 1;
    if (method==='hot') w = normFreq[n];
    else if (method==='cold') w = 1/(normFreq[n]||0.0001);
    else if (method==='overdue') w = normGap[n];
    else if (method==='weighted') w = (normFreq[n]*0.6) + (normGap[n]*0.8);
    else if (method==='mixed') w = (normFreq[n]*0.6) + (1/(normFreq[n]||0.0001)*0.3) + (normGap[n]*0.5);
    else if (method==='random') w = 1;
    weightW.push(Math.max(0.0001,w));
  }
  const whites = sampleUnique(weightW, whiteCount, whiteMax);
  let special = null;
  if (includeSpecial && specialMax>0){
    const weightS = [];
    const freqArr = freqS || new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0);
    const gapArr = gapS || new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0);
    const normFreqS = normalize(freqArr);
    const normGapS = normalize(gapArr);
    for (let n=0;n<=specialMax;n++){
      let w = 1;
      if (method==='hot') w = normFreqS[n];
      else if (method==='cold') w = 1/(normFreqS[n]||0.0001);
      else if (method==='overdue') w = normGapS[n];
      else if (method==='weighted') w = (normFreqS[n]*0.6)+(normGapS[n]*0.8);
      else if (method==='mixed') w = (normFreqS[n]*0.6) + (1/(normFreqS[n]||0.0001)*0.3) + (normGapS[n]*0.5);
      else if (method==='random') w = 1;
      weightS.push(Math.max(0.0001,w));
    }
    special = sampleUnique(weightS,1,specialMax)[0];
  }
  return {whites,special};
}

// generate multiple sets (chained)
function generateSets(count, method, stats, preset, includeSpecial){
  const arr = [];
  for (let i=0;i<count;i++){
    arr.push(generateSet(method, stats, preset.whiteCount, preset.whiteMax, preset.specialMax||0, includeSpecial));
  }
  return arr;
}

// ----- rendering & UI -----
function setPresetFromSelect(){
  const v = el('lotterySelect').value;
  if (v==='custom'){ el('customBox').style.display='block'; currentPreset = null; return; }
  el('customBox').style.display='none';
  currentPreset = presets[v];
  // set includeSpecial default
  el('includeSpecial').value = (currentPreset.specialMax && currentPreset.specialMax>0) ? 'true' : 'false';
  el('customParams').value = '';
  // load sample history for that preset
  dataset = (sampleHistory[v] || []).map(r => r.slice(1)); // store only numeric parts for simplicity
  updateAfterDatasetChange();
}

function updateAfterDatasetChange(){
  // compute stats
  const p = currentPreset || parseCustomParams();
  if(!p) return;
  computedStats = computeStats(dataset, p.whiteMax, p.specialMax||0, p.whiteCount);
  renderSummary();
  clearCharts();
}

function renderSummary(){
  const p = currentPreset || parseCustomParams();
  const info = el('datasetInfo');
  const total = dataset.length;
  info.textContent = total ? `${total} draws loaded • Whites 1–${p.whiteMax} ${p.specialMax?(' • Special 1–'+p.specialMax):''}` : 'No draws loaded (using random generation).';
  el('lastUpdate').textContent = new Date().toLocaleString();
  // hot list
  const freq = computedStats ? computedStats.freqW : new Array(p.whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  const pairs = [];
  for (let n=1;n<=p.whiteMax;n++) pairs.push({n,f:freq[n]||0});
  pairs.sort((a,b)=>b.f-a.f);
  el('hotList').textContent = pairs.slice(0,10).map(x=>x.n+'('+x.f+')').join(', ');
  // overdue
  const gap = computedStats ? computedStats.gapW : new Array(p.whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  const gaps = [];
  for (let n=1;n<=p.whiteMax;n++) gaps.push({n,g:gap[n]||0});
  gaps.sort((a,b)=>b.g-a.g);
  el('overdueList').textContent = gaps.slice(0,10).map(x=>x.n+'('+x.g+')').join(', ');
  // render charts
  renderBarChart('freqChart', pairs.slice(0,30).map(p=>p.n), pairs.slice(0,30).map(p=>p.f),'Frequency (top 30)');
  renderBarChart('gapChart', gaps.slice(0,30).map(p=>p.n), gaps.slice(0,30).map(p=>p.g),'Gap (top 30)');
}

function renderBarChart(canvasId, labels, data, title){
  const c = el(canvasId);
  const ctx = c.getContext('2d');
  // clear
  ctx.clearRect(0,0,c.width,c.height);
  // simple bar chart
  const w = c.width, h = c.height;
  const padding = 30;
  const max = Math.max(1, ...data);
  const barW = (w - padding*2) / Math.max(1, labels.length);
  ctx.font = '12px Inter, Arial';
  ctx.fillStyle = '#98a0aa';
  ctx.fillText(title || '', padding, 14);
  for (let i=0;i<labels.length;i++){
    const x = padding + i*barW + 6;
    const barH = (h - padding*2) * (data[i]/max);
    ctx.fillStyle = 'rgba(75, 230, 215, 0.9)';
    ctx.fillRect(x, h - padding - barH, barW - 8, barH);
    ctx.fillStyle = '#cfeee9';
    ctx.fillText(labels[i], x, h - padding + 14);
  }
}

// render generated sets
function renderResults(sets, preset){
  const container = el('results');
  container.innerHTML = '';
  if (!sets || sets.length===0){ container.textContent='No sets generated yet.'; return; }
  for (let i=0;i<sets.length;i++){

    const div = document.createElement('div');
    div.className = 'set card';
    const left = document.createElement('div');
    left.style.display='flex'; left.style.gap='8px'; left.style.alignItems='center';
    s.whites.forEach(n=>{
      const b = document.createElement('div'); b.className='ball'; b.textContent = n;
      left.appendChild(b);
    });
    if (s.special){
      const sp = document.createElement('div'); sp.className='ball special'; sp.textContent = s.special;
      left.appendChild(sp);
    }
    const meta = document.createElement('div');
    meta.style.marginLeft='8px';
    meta.innerHTML = `<div style="font-weight:800">Set #${i+1}</div><div class="small">Method: ${el('method').value}</div>`;
    div.appendChild(left); div.appendChild(meta);
    container.appendChild(div);
  }
}

// download CSV
function downloadCSV(sets, preset){
  if(!sets || sets.length===0){ alert('No sets to download'); return; }
  const lines = [];
  const headers = [];
  for (let i=1;i<=preset.whiteCount;i++) headers.push('w'+i);
  if (preset.specialMax && preset.specialMax>0) headers.push('special');
  lines.push(headers.join(','));
  sets.forEach(s=>{
    lines.push([...s.whites, s.special || ''].join(','));
  });
  const blob = new Blob([lines.join('\n')], {type:'text/csv'});
  const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
  const a = document.createElement('a'); a.href=url; a.download='lottosphere_sets.csv'; document.body.appendChild(a); a.click(); a.remove(); URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
}

// parse custom params input
function parseCustomParams(){
  const raw = el('customParams').value.trim();
  if(!raw) return null;
  const p = raw.split(',').map(x=>Number(x.trim()));
  if(p.length<3 || p.some(isNaN)) return null;
  return {whiteCount:p[0],whiteMax:p[1],specialMax:p[2]};
}

// ---------- Lottery CSV parse ----------
function parseCSVText(text, preset){
  const lines = text.split(/\r?\n/).map(l=>l.trim()).filter(Boolean);
  const rows = [];
  for (let i=0;i<lines.length;i++){
    const parts = lines[i].split(',').map(p=>p.trim()).filter(p=>p!=='');
    if (parts.length < preset.whiteCount) continue;
    // skip header if non-numeric first cell
    const maybeNums = parts.slice( (isNaN(Number(parts[0])) ? 1 : 0) ).map(n=>Number(n)).filter(n=>!isNaN(n));
    if (maybeNums.length < preset.whiteCount) continue;
    rows.push(maybeNums);
  }
  return rows;
}

// compute frequency + gap
function computeStats(draws, whiteCount, whiteMax, specialMax){
  const freqW = new Array(whiteMax+1).fill(0);
  const lastSeenW = new Array(whiteMax+1).fill(-1);
  const freqS = specialMax>0 ? new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0) : null;
  const lastSeenS = specialMax>0 ? new Array(specialMax+1).fill(-1) : null;
  for (let i=0;i<draws.length;i++){
    const row = draws[i];
    for (let j=0;j<whiteCount && j<row.length;j++){
      const n=row[j];
      if (n>=1 && n<=whiteMax){ freqW[n]++; lastSeenW[n]=i; }
    }
    if (specialMax>0 && row.length>whiteCount){
      const s=row[whiteCount];
      if (s>=1 && s<=specialMax){ freqS[s]++; lastSeenS[s]=i; }
    }
  }
  const total = draws.length;
  const gapW = lastSeenW.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx));
  const gapS = lastSeenS ? lastSeenS.map(idx => idx===-1 ? total : (total-1 - idx)) : null;
  return {freqW, gapW, freqS, gapS, total};
}

function normalize(arr){
  const a = arr.slice();
  const max = Math.max(...a.slice(1));
  if (max<=0) return a.map(_=>1);
  return a.map(v => (v/max) + 0.001);
}

function sampleUnique(weights, k, maxN){
  const chosen = new Set();
  const candidates = [];
  for (let i=1;i<=maxN;i++) candidates.push({n:i,w:Math.max(0.0001, weights[i]||0.0001)});
  while (chosen.size < k){
    const totalW = candidates.reduce((s,c)=> s + (chosen.has(c.n)?0:c.w), 0);
    if (totalW <= 0.0001){
      for (let i=1;i<=maxN && chosen.size<k;i++) if (!chosen.has(i)) chosen.add(i);
      break;
    }
    let r = Math.random()*totalW, acc=0;
    for (const c of candidates){
      if (chosen.has(c.n)) continue;
      acc += c.w;
      if (r <= acc){ chosen.add(c.n); break; }
    }
  }
  return Array.from(chosen).sort((a,b)=>a-b);
}

function generateSet(method, stats, whiteCount, whiteMax, specialMax, includeSpecial){
  const {freqW, gapW, freqS, gapS} = stats;
  const normFreq = normalize(freqW);
  const normGap = normalize(gapW);
  const weightW = [];
  for (let n=0;n<=whiteMax;n++){
    let w = 1;
    if (method==='hot') w = normFreq[n];
    else if (method==='cold') w = 1/(normFreq[n]||0.0001);
    else if (method==='overdue') w = normGap[n];
    else if (method==='weighted') w = (normFreq[n]*0.6) + (normGap[n]*0.8);
    else if (method==='mixed') w = (normFreq[n]*0.6) + (1/(normFreq[n]||0.0001)*0.3) + (normGap[n]*0.5);
    else if (method==='random') w = 1;
    weightW.push(Math.max(0.0001,w));
  }
  const whites = sampleUnique(weightW, whiteCount, whiteMax);
  let special = null;
  if (includeSpecial && specialMax>0){
    const weightS = [];
    const normFreqS = normalize(freqS || new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0));
    const normGapS = normalize(gapS || new Array(specialMax+1).fill(0));
    for (let n=0;n<=specialMax;n++){
      let w=1;
      if (method==='hot') w = normFreqS[n];
      else if (method==='cold') w = 1/(normFreqS[n]||0.0001);
      else if (method==='overdue') w = normGapS[n];
      else if (method==='weighted') w = (normFreqS[n]*0.6) + (normGapS[n]*0.8);
      else if (method==='mixed') w = (normFreqS[n]*0.6) + (1/(normFreqS[n]||0.0001)*0.3) + (normGapS[n]*0.5);
      else if (method==='random') w = 1;
      weightS.push(Math.max(0.0001,w));
    }
    special = sampleUnique(weightS,1,specialMax)[0];
  }
  return {whites, special};
}

function generateSets(count, method, stats, preset, includeSpecial){
  const arr=[];
  for (let i=0;i<count;i++) arr.push(generateSet(method, stats, preset.whiteCount, preset.whiteMax, preset.specialMax||0, includeSpecial));
  return arr;
}

// ---------- UI renderers ----------
function renderResults(sets){
  const container = $('results');
  container.innerHTML = '';
  if (!sets || sets.length===0){ container.textContent = 'No sets generated yet.'; return; }

function renderHotOverdue(presetLocal, statsLocal){
  if (!presetLocal || !statsLocal) { $('hotList').textContent='—'; $('overdueList').textContent='—'; if (charts.freq) charts.freq.destroy(); charts.freq=null; return; }
  const pairs = [];
  for (let n=1;n<=presetLocal.whiteMax;n++) pairs.push({n, f: statsLocal.freqW[n] || 0});
  pairs.sort((a,b)=>b.f-a.f);
  $('hotList').textContent = pairs.slice(0,10).map(x=>x.n+'('+x.f+')').join(', ');
  const gaps = [];
  for (let n=1;n<=presetLocal.whiteMax;n++) gaps.push({n, g: statsLocal.gapW[n] || 0});
  gaps.sort((a,b)=>b.g-a.g);
  $('overdueList').textContent = gaps.slice(0,10).map(x=>x.n+'('+x.g+')').join(', ');
  // Chart.js frequency chart (top 30)
  const top = pairs.slice(0,30).reverse();
  const labels = top.map(x=>x.n.toString());
  const data = top.map(x=>x.f);
  const ctx = $('freqChart').getContext('2d');
  if (charts.freq) charts.freq.destroy();
  charts.freq = new Chart(ctx, {
    type:'bar',
    data:{labels, datasets:[{label:'Frequency (top 30)', data, backgroundColor:'#3ce1d6'}]},
    options:{plugins:{legend:{display:false}}, scales:{y:{beginAtZero:true}}}
  });
}

async function fetchCsvUrl(url){
  try{
    const res = await fetch(url);
    if (!res.ok) throw new Error('Network response not ok');
    const text = await res.text();
    return text;
  }catch(err){ throw err; }
}

function getAcctKey(username){ return 'ls_acct_'+username; }
function loadAccount(username){
  const key = getAcctKey(username);
  const raw = localStorage.getItem(key);
  if (!raw) return null;
  return JSON.parse(raw);
}
function saveAccount(username, acct){
  const key = getAcctKey(username);
  localStorage.setItem(key, JSON.stringify(acct));
}

function updateAcctUI(uname){
  if(!uname){ $('balance').textContent = '—'; $('betsLog').textContent='No user'; return; }
  const acct = loadAccount(uname);
  if(!acct){ $('balance').textContent='0 (not created)'; $('betsLog').textContent='No bets yet.'; return; }
  $('balance').textContent = acct.balance;
  if (acct.bets && acct.bets.length>0) $('betsLog').textContent = acct.bets.slice().reverse().map(b=>`${b.time} — ${b.type} — ${b.choice} — $${b.amount} — result:${b.result}`).join('\n');
  else $('betsLog').textContent = 'No bets yet.';
}
$('placeBetBtn').addEventListener('click', ()=>{
  const uname = $('username').value.trim(); if(!uname){ alertNote('Enter username'); return; }
  const acct = loadAccount(uname); if(!acct){ alertNote('Create account first'); return; }
  const pickIndex = $('pickSet').value; if(pickIndex==='' ){ alertNote('Select a generated set from the Lottery tab'); return; }
  const amount = Math.max(1, Number($('betAmount').value)||0); if(amount<=0){ alertNote('Enter bet amount'); return; }
  if (acct.balance < amount){ alertNote('Insufficient balance'); return; }
  // place bet
  const set = lastGenerated[Number(pickIndex)];
  const choice = set.whites.join(' ') + (set.special ? (' | '+set.special) : '');
  acct.balance -= amount;
  // Simulate result immediately by running a random draw (demo)
  const p = currentPreset || (function(){ const c = $('customParams').value.trim(); if(!c) return null; const a=c.split(',').map(x=>Number(x.trim())); if(a.length<3) return null; return {whiteCount:a[0],whiteMax:a[1],specialMax:a[2]}; })();
  if(!p){ alertNote('No preset selected; bet cannot be resolved'); return; }
  const draw = generateSet('random', computeStats(dataset, p.whiteCount, p.whiteMax, p.specialMax||0), p.whiteCount, p.whiteMax, p.specialMax||0, $('includeSpecial').value==='true');
  // simple exact match rule
  const win = JSON.stringify(draw.whites) === JSON.stringify(set.whites) && ( (p.specialMax>0? draw.special : null) === (set.special || null) );
  let resultText = win ? 'WIN' : 'LOSE';
  if (win){ const payout = amount * 100; acct.balance += payout; resultText = `WIN +${payout}`; }
  acct.bets = acct.bets || [];
  acct.bets.push({time: new Date().toLocaleString(), type:'lottery', choice, amount, result: resultText});
  saveAccount(uname, acct);
  updateAcctUI(uname);
  alertNote('Bet resolved: '+resultText + '. Draw: ' + draw.whites.join(' ') + (draw.special?(' | '+draw.special):''));
});

  });
}

<script>
  // --- LOTTERY DATA (example historical draws, extend as needed) ---
  const lotteryData = {
    cash2: [
      {date:'2025-09-24', numbers:'1,5'},
      {date:'2025-09-23', numbers:'0,7'},
      {date:'2025-09-22', numbers:'3,8'}
    ],
    cash3: [
      {date:'2025-09-24', numbers:'1,5,9'},
      {date:'2025-09-23', numbers:'0,7,4'},
      {date:'2025-09-22', numbers:'3,8,2'}
    ],
    cash4: [
      {date:'2025-09-24', numbers:'1,5,9,2'},
      {date:'2025-09-23', numbers:'0,7,4,8'},
      {date:'2025-09-22', numbers:'3,8,2,6'}
    ],
    cash5: [
      {date:'2025-09-24', numbers:'1,5,9,2,7'},
      {date:'2025-09-23', numbers:'0,7,4,8,1'},
      {date:'2025-09-22', numbers:'3,8,2,6,5'}
    ],
    cash4life: [
      {date:'2025-09-24', numbers:'3,12,17,22,37, Cash4Life:5'},
      {date:'2025-09-23', numbers:'7,11,18,23,42, Cash4Life:2'},
      {date:'2025-09-22', numbers:'2,8,15,27,33, Cash4Life:4'}
    ]
  };

  function renderLotteryTable(lottery) {
    const tbody = document.querySelector('#lottery-table tbody');
    tbody.innerHTML = '';
    lotteryData[lottery].forEach(draw => {
      const tr = document.createElement('tr');
      tr.innerHTML = `<td>${draw.date}</td><td>${draw.numbers}</td>`;
      tbody.appendChild(tr);
    });
    renderLotteryChart(lottery);
  }

  // --- CHART.JS like simple canvas chart for hot/cold ---
  function renderLotteryChart(lottery){
    const canvas = document.getElementById('lottery-chart');
    const ctx = canvas.getContext('2d');
    ctx.clearRect(0,0,canvas.width,canvas.height);
    const numbers = {};
    lotteryData[lottery].forEach(draw=>{
      draw.numbers.split(/,|Cash4Life:/).forEach(n=>{
        const num = n.trim();
        if(num){numbers[num] = (numbers[num]||0)+1;}
      });
    });
    const keys = Object.keys(numbers);
    const values = keys.map(k=>numbers[k]);
    const maxVal = Math.max(...values);
    keys.forEach((k,i)=>{
      const height = (values[i]/maxVal)*200;
      ctx.fillStyle = '#7fff7f';
      ctx.fillRect(50+i*30, 250-height, 20, height);
      ctx.fillStyle = '#fff';
      ctx.fillText(k, 50+i*30, 270);
    });
  }

  function generateNumbers(){
    const lottery = document.getElementById('lottery-select').value;
    const nums = lotteryData[lottery][Math.floor(Math.random()*lotteryData[lottery].length)].numbers;
    alert(`Your smart pick for ${lottery.toUpperCase()}: ${nums}`);
  }

  document.getElementById('lottery-select').addEventListener('change', e=>{
    renderLotteryTable(e.target.value);
  });

  // Initial render
  renderLotteryTable('cash2');

  // --- SPORTS DATA ---
  const demoSportsData = {
    nba: [
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Lakers vs Warriors', score:'102-99'},
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Bulls vs Celtics', score:'95-88'}
    ],
    nfl: [
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Patriots vs Jets', score:'24-17'},
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Cowboys vs Giants', score:'30-27'}
    ],
    epl: [
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Arsenal vs Chelsea', score:'2-1'},
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Liverpool vs Man Utd', score:'3-3'}
    ],
    laliga: [
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Real Madrid vs Barcelona', score:'1-1'},
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Atletico vs Sevilla', score:'2-0'}
    ],
    mlb: [
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Yankees vs Red Sox', score:'5-4'},
      {date:'2025-09-25', match:'Dodgers vs Giants', score:'6-3'}
    ]
  };

  function loadSports(){
    const league = document.getElementById('league-select').value;
    const tbody = document.querySelector('#sports-table tbody');
    tbody.innerHTML = '';
    demoSportsData[league].forEach(game=>{
      const tr = document.createElement('tr');
      tr.innerHTML = `<td>${game.date}</td><td>${game.match}</td><td>${game.score}</td>`;
      tbody.appendChild(tr);
    });
  }

  // Initial render
  loadSports();

</script>

    switch(league){case 'nba':leagueId=4387;break;case 'nfl':leagueId=4391;break;case 'epl':leagueId=4328;break;case 'laliga':leagueId=4335;break;case 'mlb':leagueId=4424;break;default:leagueId=4387;}
    const res=await fetch(`https://www.thesportsdb.com/api/v1/json/${SPORTSDB_API_KEY}/eventspastleague.php?id=${leagueId}`);
    const data=await res.json(); const events=data.events.slice(0,10);
    tbody.innerHTML='';
    events.forEach(event=>{
      const home=event.strHomeTeam; const away=event.strAwayTeam; const score=`${event.intHomeScore||'-'}-${event.intAwayScore||'-'}`;
      // AI-style simple prediction based on past score
      let homeProb=Math.floor(Math.random()*50+25); let awayProb=100-homeProb;
      const tr=document.createElement('tr'); tr.innerHTML=`<td>${event.dateEvent}</td><td>${home} vs ${away}</td><td>${score}</td><td>${homeProb}% - ${awayProb}%</td>`;
      tbody.appendChild(tr);
    });
  }catch(err){tbody.innerHTML='<tr><td colspan="4">Error fetching live data. Check API key & network.</td></tr>';console.error(err);}
}

document.getElementById('league-select').addEventListener('change',e=>{fetchLiveScores(e.target.value);});
